Below you will find current food-access points across the La Plata, Archuleta, and San Juan Counties. This list is not comprehensive - it is currently in the works and will be edited each day to reflect additional verified data. It is live, so edits will be visible as soon as they are made. This information is subject to change, as organizations and stores may change their hours and the services they are able to provide. 

You can find free and reduced-cost food by searching the nonprofit organization table, and locations to buy food by searching the retail table. 


You can find additional resources by calling either of the bilingual free hotlines below, or by searching this State Guide.
